column5: I am Gravyboat.  I like to fish, so I joined this site.  Just saying hi!

Hi gravyboat and welcome to the board, glad you joined! Where are you from, what do you like to fish for, tell us a little about yourself, it'll help you hook up with like minded people on the board. Oh and pictures, we love pictures!
Welcome, i joined not to long ago and it has been greate here. Nice people and pages of good information. Enjoy your summer.
With a handle like that yer gonna make us all hungry!! Welcome aboard!
Welcome to the board!  Hope you enjoy your time here!
I make really good gravy myself!  Welcome!
welcome to the board and enjoy
Welcome to the board!  You meet all the pre qualifications.
Welcome to the board.   Lots of pics please.
welcome aboard its a good place to be, it's kinda like cheers (the bar) eventually u get to know everybody's name
He joined us last spring lol, check the original post. I was wondeirng why someone posted "have a nice summer". Someone was feeling silly and bumped the thread for some reason lol
I guess none of us except you Blaque noticed it..... Will have to pay attention to the dates from now on
HAHAHA... this is such an old thread HAHAHA  HI!
